### Health Check
GET https://<your-app-name>.azurewebsites.net/health

### ============================================
### TEST 1: Failed Login Attempts (Should generate warning logs)
### ============================================

### Failed attempt 1 - wrong password
POST https://<your-app-name>.azurewebsites.net/login?username=attacker&password=wrongpassword

### Failed attempt 2 - wrong password
POST https://<your-app-name>.azurewebsites.net/login?username=attacker&password=wrongpassword2

### Failed attempt 3 - wrong password
POST https://<your-app-name>.azurewebsites.net/login?username=attacker&password=wrongpassword3

### Failed attempt 4 - wrong password
POST https://<your-app-name>.azurewebsites.net/login?username=attacker&password=wrongpassword4

### Failed attempt 5 - wrong password
POST https://<your-app-name>.azurewebsites.net/login?username=attacker&password=wrongpassword5

### Failed attempt 6 - wrong password (This should trigger the alert if threshold is 5)
POST https://<your-app-name>.azurewebsites.net/login?username=attacker&password=wrongpassword6

### ============================================
### TEST 2: Successful Login Attempts
### ============================================

### Successful login - admin
POST https://<your-app-name>.azurewebsites.net/login?username=admin&password=supersecret

### Successful login - alice
POST https://<your-app-name>.azurewebsites.net/login?username=alice&password=password123

### ============================================
### TEST 3: Missing Credentials (Should also log as warning)
### ============================================

### Missing username
POST https://<your-app-name>.azurewebsites.net/login?password=test

### Missing password
POST https://<your-app-name>.azurewebsites.net/login?username=test

### ============================================
### TEST 4: Multiple Failed Attempts with Different Usernames
### ============================================

### Failed attempts for different users (should not trigger alert individually)
POST https://<your-app-name>.azurewebsites.net/login?username=user1&password=wrong
POST https://<your-app-name>.azurewebsites.net/login?username=user2&password=wrong
POST https://<your-app-name>.azurewebsites.net/login?username=user3&password=wrong
POST https://<your-app-name>.azurewebsites.net/login?username=user4&password=wrong
POST https://<your-app-name>.azurewebsites.net/login?username=user5&password=wrong